{"tid":2408804,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★Ready！張建宗：圍封行動有效 過年後或再做！！","createTime":"2021-02-15T09:20:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T12:52:11.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ca08da0c344e9350c99b99592d3b025c9da71671","tid":2408804,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T09:20:16.000Z","msg":"政務司司長張建宗指圍封行動有效，不排除視乎疫情，農曆新年後再做；又指若確診數字維持單位數，可以有條件恢復通關，不排除疫苗是其中一個考慮通關的條件。<br />\n<br />\n過去多日，全港多區的圍封行動確診比率百分之0.08。政務司司長張建宗強調，數字不低、有成效，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>形容措施是戰略調整，又不排除會再做。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.tvb.com/local/60278372335d19e64554d0ea/%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97%E7%A8%B1%E5%9C%8D%E5%B0%81%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88-%E8%A6%96%E4%B9%8E%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E9%81%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%BE%8C%E6%88%96%E5%86%8D%E5%81%9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F60278372335d19e64554d0ea%2F%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%25AE%2597%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E5%259C%258D%25E5%25B0%2581%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2595%2588-%25E8%25A6%2596%25E4%25B9%258E%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BE%258C%25E6%2588%2596%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%2581%259A&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4eWWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=557ed16b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.tvb.com/local/60278372335d19e64554d0ea/%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97%E7%A8%B1%E5%9C%8D%E5%B0%81%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88-%E8%A6%96%E4%B9%8E%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E9%81%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%BE%8C%E6%88%96%E5%86%8D%E5%81%9A</a>"},{"pid":"8141ec3092c260aead2a093043afe87de75e8e8b","tid":2408804,"uid":19454,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T09:20:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BQHBMCd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBQHBMCd.jpg&h=41c415c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56d93a596997691e7e3dbf1dc91943dd69d2ef06","tid":2408804,"uid":304916,"like":0,"disl